The main idea of this project is to detect harmful gases present in air and let the user to move in a safe path.

Step 1: Connecting mq 135 and gsm module to arduino

Step 2: Copy the code from GSM_module.ino (Replace the value of x woth your phone number)

Step 3: Change the value of R0 from AIR_MONITOR.ino

Step 4: Check the value of CO2 by dumping the code into ARDUINO
